---
title: Black Bean Tofu Tostadas with Pico de Gallo & Lime Crema
description: Toast to the tostada! The perfect marriage of your favorite taco and the satisfying crunch-factor of a plate of nachos. First, toast up your tortillas for a flat, golden, crispy base. Then, layer on all the toppings—creamy refried black beans, warmly-spiced, protein-packed tofu crumbles, melty Mexican cheeses, homemade pico de gallo, and tangy lime crema. Yep, it’s pretty safe to say these tostadas are perfectly crunch-tastic! Cheers!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/black-bean-tofu-tostadas-60b8a9e9.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/black-bean-tofu-tostadas-6329e95e15ed8de8440f88eb-0d4df727.pdf
